SUMMARY:Bull City Block Party
DESCRIPTION:We’re back in Durham for the Bull City Block Party!! Shutting down the street for some food\, drinks\, games\, music\, and of course some sick vintage shopping. It’s FREE ADMISSION\, so tell a friend and we’ll see you soon at Durham Central Park!
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/bull-city-block-party-2/
LOCATION:The Pavilion\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://durhamcentralpark.org/content/uploads/BCBP-print-flyer2026-scaled.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Secondhand Concession Stand":MAILTO:2ndhandconcessionstand@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
