SUMMARY:Foodie Fare
DESCRIPTION:The MAKRS Society presents: Durham Foodie Fare: a foodie and art market.\nShowcasing Durham’s diverse food and art scene.\nCalling all Foodies!! Join us for our monthly foodie and art market series featuring a food truck rodeo\, food vendors\, and art vendors. Grab drinks from The Glass Jug next door!\nLocation: Durham Central Park\nEvent time: 5:30pm-9:30pm\n\nGrab delicious foods\, drinks and more. And make memories with your friends and family!\nMore info on this event: https://makrs.com/durham-foodie-fare\nInterested in being a vendor? You can apply to any of our events here! https://makrs.com/market-applications
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/foodie-fare/2026-05-15/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="MAKRS Society":MAILTO:max@makrs.com
END:VEVENT
